data.description: Adorable main level living located just minutes from Lynchburg. Home sits on a nice level lot with plenty of parking space. The inside features a great flowy layout with 3 bedrooms. Updates include fresh paint and new flooring. This home is great for first time home buyers or anyone looking to downsize. Plenty of room in the backyard for kids and pets and social gatherings. Located just minutes from local grocery stores and restaurants.
